com.keenant.tabbed.tablist

Class TableTabList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.keenant.tabbed.tablist.TitledTabList
      • com.keenant.tabbed.tablist.SimpleTabList
        • com.keenant.tabbed.tablist.TableTabList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CustomTabList, TabList

    public class TableTabList
extends SimpleTabList
    An implementation of SimpleTabList that behaves like an HTML/CSS table. It has columns and rows where (0,0) is the top left and (columns - 1, rows - 1) is the top right. It supports some fancy operations like filling a portion of the table in any direction.
